Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,海崎的ReLIFE就快要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.84,0:00:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這一年對我來說一定也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.99,0:00:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,船到橋頭自然直
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,無論結果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,都不用再重考了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.46,0:00:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我想開心畢業  你加油好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可是都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只有海崎留級了  真心疼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,海崎真正遇到危機的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:00:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就會像這樣很消沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這是在模仿我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,和新太一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,海崎的ReLIFE是個成功的案例
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事已經傳達到總部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,之後  他即將迎接28歲的現實人生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.75,0:01:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我會不告訴他某件重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,結束這場ReLIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.88,0:01:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我無法直接向他道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是覺得很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:44.50,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord0\shad0\an7\c&H7D7C70&\frz17.11\pos(774.133,339.865)}今晚似乎會非常冷\N記得要保暖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:44.50,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord0\shad0\an7\c&H7D7C70&\frz17.11\pos(479.467,551.866)}好的\N謝謝關心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:45.50,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord0\shad0\an7\c&H7D7C70&\frz17.11\fad(42,0)\pos(386.134,281.199)}好的\N謝謝關心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord0\shad0\an7\c&H7D7C70&\frz17.11\fad(84,0)\pos(472.8,559.866)}那麼\N明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:02:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,能在學校見面的時間已經不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不只是想在LIME上講話  其實還想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  明明都和你道過晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,話說  怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那個  雖然不是什麼重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我也想聽聽你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,聽到你的聲音  我就能放心睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊  那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:02:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,還能和他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,說幾次這句話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你們的人生旅途才剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,以後可能會遇到許多不如意的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不過  就算真的不如意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,只要再試一次就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,人生的路那麼長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就算繞點遠路也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,人啊  多繞點路才更好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,腳踏實地  不畏前方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,抬頭挺胸  活出自我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\bord0\shad0\pos(641.333,515.333)\c&HA19B8D&}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,新太想說的只有這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺好沒誠意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高興能認識你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,之所以能一起畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,都是多虧大神的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,小玉  你這話說得太直接了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:40.13,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord0\shad0\c&HA19B8D&\move(1116,114,1251,114)}我在青葉長了30公分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:40.13,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord0\shad0\c&HA19B8D&\move(827,225,965,225)}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:40.13,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord0\shad0\an7\c&HA19B8D&\move(993,399,1128,399)}我最喜歡大家了\N\h                穗香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不過海崎還真努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,大家能一起畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真的讓我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,別哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛天津老師哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正准圆_GBK\fs30\frz270\fax-0.1\bord0\shad0\an7\c&HE1DFDD&\pos(722,130)}感謝大家一直以來的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,驚喜超成功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多該回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,日代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,海崎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,確切感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你告訴我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好好享受當下的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一直留在我的腦海裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,給我獎勵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼獎勵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼  你可以抱緊我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,日代也要交很多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,談場美妙的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,海崎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,以前好像也發生過這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那個  那個時候只是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你還是別忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你別忘了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我絕對不會忘記你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你會忘掉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我是實驗對象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以海崎會忘掉有關我的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我們同樣都是實驗對象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,因此  海崎也會從我記憶中消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不想忘掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會忘掉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不會忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我能保持這個姿勢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在沒辦法見人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,明明不是就此別離了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你說謊的時候就像呼吸一樣自然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟我們升了大學還是能在一起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你的謊言總是善意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,今天你的ReLIFE就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,總部判斷  會按照之前約定好的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,幫你介紹幾個工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,到時候你可以好好考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,ReLIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,新太  真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,派對從傍晚才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒辦法去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我還有其他事要辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼  我們下次見面的時候就是開學典禮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,新太  春天的時候再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他們笑得非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道該怎麼說下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,反正自己以後就會被忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我當時應該回應他們的期待才對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我想在最後留下回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我打從一開始就是個不存在的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你在這場ReLIFE和許多人有來往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,留下了很多證明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不只有你享有這份經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,大神  狩生  玉來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,還有日代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這些經歷也會成為大家往後的心靈支柱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,如果這一年過得很開心  那就更不用說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,拿出自信來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的經歷了一場很棒的ReLIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,做好心理準備了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我必須在場見證
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我會一直陪你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我早在一年前就做好心理準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你的ReLIFE真的很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,海崎  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,別搶走我的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.91,0:10:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我必須在場見證
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,所以直到你做好心理準備為止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我都會一直陪你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我的ReLIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這次是不是真的成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,當然成功了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是真的成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要等你變回大人  再靠自己來證明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你的ReLIFE就是為了這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真愛說教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,最後就讓我說教一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,吃下這顆藥就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但實際上和人來往  再和他們別離
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺自己的心被挖了一個洞  好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定我的ReLIFE不能算是成功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但也不是像  要是沒遇見他們該多好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我感覺自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,應該改變了一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,日代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,代我向了道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:11:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,日代  我差不多要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,起藥效了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,日代已經熟睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我也差不多要離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,小野屋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你幫了日代很多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我有點忌妒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,日代要我轉達
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她對我還是很冷淡的說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她沒有完全提到海崎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就算她找你商量事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我們還是要消除實驗對象的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我們也沒辦法幫到他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:12:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小野屋  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,日代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣不就會被我發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:25.70,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1008,0)}我喜歡上了海崎新太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我知道了這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我如何置之不理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,做事要謹慎一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就算ReLIFE結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,和告知的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這一年的記憶還留著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是在ReLIFE掛上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但就算我百般回想  也想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,夜明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,請說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我去找其他的工作也沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這其中沒有你有興趣的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這些工作是我們精挑細選出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我想在ReLIFE研究所工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,ReLIFE讓我了解到很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是平凡無奇的日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但藉由和年輕人之間的相處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,還有從不同角度來看待事物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我了解到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是看似平凡的生活也是很有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在這一年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我察覺到日常生活中不會發現的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然只有一年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你想做一份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,能把自己的經歷告訴其他人的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.74,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\bord0\shad0\an7\c&H7B7671&\b0\pos(391,117)}好過分\N連海崎都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.74,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\bord0\shad0\an7\c&H7B7671&\b0\pos(821,302)}好啦好啦\N再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.74,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\bord0\shad0\an7\c&H7B7671&\b0\pos(337,403.333)}這次的酒會\N因為我們是高中生\N所以沒辦法去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:35.24,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\bord0\shad0\an7\c&H7B7671&\b0\pos(844,144)}好啦好啦\N再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:35.24,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\bord0\shad0\an7\c&H7B7671&\b0\pos(359.667,245)}這次的酒會\N因為我們是高中生\N所以沒辦法去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:35.24,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\bord0\shad0\an7\c&H7B7671&\b0\pos(318.334,594.333)}你要好好享受喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:36.29,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\bord0\shad0\an7\c&H7B7671&\b0\pos(395.667,0)}這次的酒會\N因為我們是高中生\N所以沒辦法去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:36.29,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\bord0\shad0\an7\c&H7B7671&\b0\pos(354.334,335.666)}你要好好享受喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:41.29,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\bord0\shad0\an7\c&H7B7671&\pos(320,528)}你今天要去的吧\N加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我們有請您的家人幫我們轉達過這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉  今天突然來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我想請你參加一場實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不滿意現在的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在這場實驗中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你會再次體驗自己的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你要不要ReLIFE呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺很難融入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,新人  開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好餓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡是我的位子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:18:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒用過  你用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛好被叫到那邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我很期待原本是實驗對象的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是剛剛遇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,因為下雨了  所以大家急忙跑去續攤了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟明天還要早起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我絕對不是在避免和他人交流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,因為上司說過  新人最好別來續攤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,借你用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不用啦  這樣我不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛上司好像說你是實驗對象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我去年有經歷ReLIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒把這件事保密起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟是個人資料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是不會在公司張揚才對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我因為經歷了ReLIFE  才有了現在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,反正早就被支援課的大家知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,或許是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我不想受到奇怪的騷擾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不公開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我是個不好的案例
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,經歷了兩年ReLIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:20:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一樣不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是公司介紹你來這裡工作的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然介紹列表沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,之後  因為負責人的極力推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,剛好也和原本的工作類型有點類似
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我就到開發研究部的藥劑課工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以問你感覺如何嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,RELIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我不太會簡單敘述
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,大概就是像煙火一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我和朋友去看過煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事讓我印象很深
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,當時玩得非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是結束之後倍感空虛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.19,0:22:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然既華麗又漂亮  讓人看得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可是當消失的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,現在回想起來有點不捨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,ReLIFE就像煙火一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,…就像煙火一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,煙火有點悲傷的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.93,0:22:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,消失的時候很空虛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.48,0:22:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,煙火的確會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.07,0:22:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,回憶卻會留下來
